-- MOVES-Edison Investment hires Mark Williams from RR Donnelley
-- 
-- Wed Oct 08, 2014 05:24AM EDT
-- None



Oct 8 (Reuters) - Investment research company Edison Investment Research named Mark Williams as global sales and marketing director and Toby Belsom and Toby Barrow as account managers to its UK sales team.

Williams joins from RR Donnelley <RRD.O> where he was the sales director and managing director for Europe. Belsom joins from Aviva Investors where he was a UK equities portfolio manager for nine years and an equities analyst for eight years.